resources.resid-settings-helpNoInternetMessage: Ukuze uthole usizo ngalo mkhiqizo, kumele uxhumeke kwi-Inthanethi. Uma uxhumekile kwi-Inthanethi futhi ubona lo myalezo ngephutha, ungase uvakashele ingosi yosizo ngokuqondile ngokuchofoza isihlanganisi esilandelayo:
resources.resid-settings-endUserAgreementLink: I-Windows 8 noma Isivumelwano Selayisensi Yomsebenzisi se-Windows RT
resources.resid-settings-endUserAgreement: I-{{%1}} igunyaza ukusebenzisa kwakho le softhiwe.
resources.resid-settings-manageOnlineLinkTooltipTe: Phatha indlela i-{{%1}} exhumeke ngayo ku-akhawunti yakho ye-Microsoft
resources.resid-settings-signOutConfirmationText:
Uqinisekile ukuthi ufuna ukukhipha i-akhawunti yakho ye-Microsoft, kuhlanganise nalo lonke ulwazi lwayo, kusuka kulolu hlelo?

Azikho izithombe noma amavidiyo akho azosuswa, kodwa ngeke zisavela futhi ohlelweni.
resources.resid-settings-signOutMessage: Ukushintsha noma ukukhipha le akhawunti, iya kokuthi Abasebenzisi kumasethingi e-PC.
resources.resid-singleSourceSelectionErrorFmt: Usuvele ukhethe amafayela kusuka kwi- {{%1}}, futhi ungakwazi ukukhetha amafayela asuka kumthombo owodwa ngesikhathi esisodwa. Uma ungathanda ukukhetha le fayela, sula okukhethile bese uzama futhi.
resources.resid-picker-deviceVideo: Awukwazi ukukhetha amavidiyo agcinwe kwenye idivaysi.
resources.resid-picker-unsupportedType: Lolu hlelo alukwazi ukuvula amafayela e-{{%1}}.
resources.resid-multiUpSlideshow-NoPhotoError: Azikho izithombe ezanele zesihlanganisi sesithombe. Engeze ezengeziwe bese uzama futhi.
resources.resid-playTo-genericFileError: Kunokuthize okungahambanga kahle, futhi asikwazi ukudlala le fayela.
resources.resid-playTo-statusFlyoutText: Ukuze umise ukudlala kombukiso wamasilaydi, indawo ethi Amadivayisi bese uyanqamula.
resources.resid-search-notIndexedMessageLine2: Khetha ifolda ehlukile bese uzama futhi.
resources.resid-search-notIndexedMessageLine1: Uxolo, asikwazi ukucinga le folda ngoba ayinayo inkomba.
resources.resid-search-emptyRemoteSearchMessageLin: Asikwazi ukucinga i-{{%1}}. Zama umtapo wakho weZithombe okhona.
resources.residSignInErrorFlyoutTextGenericFmt: Kukhona okungahambanga kahle. Sicela uphinde uzame kamuva. {{%1}}
resources.residSignInErrorFlyoutTextNoInternet: Qiniseka ukuthi uxhumeke kwi-Inthanethi bese uzama ukungena futhi ngemvume.
resources.residConnectUpsellFlyoutText: Ungase ubone izithombe kanye namavidiyo kusuka kumadivaysi akho, amasevisi, kanye nezokuxhumana konke endaweni eyodwa. Ukuze uqalise, qiniseka ukuthi uxhumeke kwi-Inthanethi.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_EmptySourceView: Yonke imithombo yezithombe zakho ifihliwe. Ukuze uveze eminye, shintsha amasethingi akho.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_GenericDevice:
Uhlelo Lwezithombe lukubonisa izithombe namavidiyo asuka kuwo wonke amadivaysi asendaweni eyodwa.

Ukuze ubone izithombe namavidiyo kwenye i-PC, yiya kuleyo PC, yiya kokuthi SkyDrive.com/windows ukuze ulayishe futhi ufake i-Microsoft SkyDrive, sayinela ukungena nge-akhawunti yakho ye-Microsoft, futhi uqinisekise ukuthi ukhetha i-Thatha amafayela akho noma yikuphi isethingi.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_Device: Uma kukhona onazo, qiniseka ukuthi uzihlanganise kumtapo Wezithombe we- {{%1}}.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_Service: Engeza ezinye izithombe kwi-akhawunti yakho ukuze uqalise.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_SkyDrive:
I-SkyDrive ikunikeza indawo yokubeka izithombe mahhala ku-inthanethi, amavidiyo namadokhumenti ukuze ukwazi ukukufinyelela noma kuphi.

Yiya ku- SkyDrive.com ukuze uqalise. Noma yiziphi izithombe namavidiyo okugcina lapho kuzoboniswa lapha.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_PicturesLibrary:
Ukuze uqalise, xhuma idivayisi (ikhamera, ifoni, ifleshi drayivu ye-USB, nokunye), bese ungenisa noma ukopishe izithombe namavidiyo emtapweni wakho weZithombe.

Uma usunazo kakade izithombe noma amavidiyo kule PC, qiniseka ukuthi zisemtapweni wakho weZithombe. Ungakwazi ukulawula umtapo wakho weZithombe ku-File Explorer.
resources.residCurrentlySyncingContent-extraInfo: Lokhu kungase kuthathe isikhathi uma unezithombe eziningi.
resources.residErrorSourceUnavailableMessageFmt: Ungakwazi ukubona ezinye izithombe kanye namavidiyo, kodwa mhlawumbe hayi okwamanje. Ukubuyekeza kokugcina kade kungezi-{{%1}}.
resources.residDeviceLimitReachedErrorInstructionT: Kunamadivayisi amaningi kakhulu axhunywe ku-akhawunti yakho, ngakho ungase ungakwazi ukubona ezinye zezithombe zakho namavidiyo agcinwe kwezinye izindawo kulolu hlelo lokusebenza. {{%1}}
resources.residErrorServiceRemovedInstructionFmt: {{%1}} ayisaxhumekile kwi-akhawunti ye-Microsoft. Uma ufuna ukuqhubeka ubona okuqukethwe kusuka kwi-{{%1}}, xhuma futhi.
resources.residErrorUpgradeableFailureInstructionT: Xhuma futhi ukuze ubuyekeze i-akhawunti yakho.
resources.residErrorGenericFailureInstructionText: Kuvele inkinga. Zama futhi emva kwesikhathi.
resources.residErrorDeviceOfflineInstructionText: Iya ku-{{%1}} futhi uqiniseke ukuthi ivuliwe futhi ixhumeke kwi-Inthanethi. Thepha noma qhafaza uphawu lwe-SkyDrive kwindawo yezaziso (ngokwesokudla sebha yomsebenzi), khetha okuthi Amasethingi, futhi uqiniseke ukuthi isethingi ethi Thatha amafayela ikhethiwe kwithebhu ethi Okuvamile tab.
resources.residErrorNoNetworkConnectionInstruction: Awukwazi ukuxhuma kwi-Inthanethi okwamanje. Sicela uzame futhi emva kwesikhathi.
resources.residErrorInvalidTimestampInstructionTex: Qiniseka ukuthi iwashi eliku-PC yakho linembile bese uphinde uzame.

photo.residAppDescription: Uhlelo lweZithombe luhlanganisa endaweni eyodwa zonke izithombe kanye namamuvi asekhaya.
